类 ClientInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ClientInfo

  • public class ClientInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to present the information of the client containing fields like firstName, lastName, companyName, address, city, county, state, zip, phonePrimary, phoneSecondary, email, web.
